# ── Frontend (Vite) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# This is a SEPARATE key from server/.env's MAPTILER_API_KEY — Vite only
# exposes env vars to the browser bundle if they're prefixed with VITE_.
# Without this, the map silently falls back to the free Carto basemap
# instead of MapTiler streets tiles (no crash, just plainer tiles).
# Put the same MapTiler key here as in server/.env.
VITE_MAPTILER_API_KEY=your-maptiler-api-key
